<div id="outline-container-org74b6ea9" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org74b6ea9">Main topics</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org74b6ea9">
<p>
At LIMSI, I'm working in the <a href="https://www.limsi.fr/fr/recherche/tlp">Spoken Language Processing group</a> and more precisely in the topic <a href="https://www.limsi.fr/en/research/tlp/topics/topic5">Machine Learning and Automatic Translation</a>. My main topics are Neural Machine Translation and language modelling. 
</p>

<p>
On the Machine learning side, I'm interested in Deep-Learning (as quite everyone but I've started earlier), Bayesian modeling (parametric and non-parametric), Conditional Random Fields, &#x2026; 
</p>
</div>
</div>



